      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project or a budget-friendly fixer-upper? This vehicle is in poor condition and is ready for someone with a mechanical touch to bring it back to its former glory! It's a great opportunity for a DIY enthusiast looking for a bargain entry into vehicle ownership.",
      "price": 6500.0,
