      "description": "This vehicle represents a distinguished opportunity for the discerning driver, offering a refined balance of performance and long-term reliability. Meticulously maintained and subjected to a comprehensive multi-point inspection, it exhibits a standard of mechanical integrity and aesthetic presentation that exceeds expectations for its class. We invite you to experience an automobile that delivers both a sophisticated driving dynamic and the assurance of professional curation.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
